hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I sing in a choir progressive yoga thierry Kate Middleton has long been a fan of the label, and the burgundy dress she wore a year ago is one of our favourites. The subtle V neck flatters her bust (without revealing too much - she is a Royal after all) and the floaty fabric gives slim Kate some curves. Note how she's swapped the gold belt for a wider black belt to match her shoes. Top marks for attention to detail as always, Duchess.
